'''Genesys''' (简称为'''Genesys''')专业面向大、中小各种规模的企业，提供客户体验与客戶联络中心方案<ref name=sfbizjournals>{{cite web|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/sanfrancisco/print-edition/2014/03/07/tech-firm-ipo-five9-gopro-glam-media.html?page=all|title=To go, or not to go: Tech's IPO shuffle|author=Patrick Hoge|publisher=San Francisco Business Times|date=2014-03-14|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006174416/http://www.bizjournals.com/sanfrancisco/print-edition/2014/03/07/tech-firm-ipo-five9-gopro-glam-media.html?page=all|dead-url=no}}</ref> 包括云及自建部署的客服平台软件。Genesys的总部设在美国加州达利市、<ref name=sfbizjournals/> 并在加拿大、南美洲、欧洲、中东、非洲和亚洲设有分公司。Genesys 成立于1990并在2012年2月被Permira 基金收购。<ref name=sfbizjournals2/><ref name=forbes>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/forbes/1998/0706/6201146a.html|title=The Russia house|author=Scott McCormack|publisher=''[[Forbes|Forbes]]''|date=1998-07-06|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2015-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150504120006/http://www.forbes.com/forbes/1998/0706/6201146a.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 由Paul Segre 引领的该公司自2007年开始到2014年已有每年7亿4千万美金的营收。<ref name=sfbizjournals2/>

==历史==
[[File:Genesys_Telecommunications_Laboratories_HQ.jpg|thumb]]
Genesys 是由Gregory Shenkman 和 Alec Miloslavsky于1990年10月所创立。<ref name=forbes/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1036436/0000929624-97-000384.txt|title=Genesys Telecommunications Laboratories, Inc.|publisher=Securities and Exchange Commission|year=1997|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2014-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140524020657/http://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1036436/0000929624-97-000384.txt|dead-url=no}}</ref> 公司最初的创业基金是来自于创业者家族贷款的15万美金。<ref name=forbes/> Genesys 于1997年6月完成首次公开募股 (IPO) 并以股票代码GCTI在纳斯达克证券交易所上市。同年12月，Genesys收购邮件管理软件开发商"Forte Software, Inc."（后改名Adante）。<ref>{{cite news|title=Finance: Call Center House Forte is now Adante after Acquisition|date=1998-03-24|publisher=Network Briefing}}</ref> 1999年6月，该公司还收购了劳动力管理软件开发商。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1036436/000092962499001769/0000929624-99-001769.txt|title=Form 10-K|publisher=Securities and Exchange Commission|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2014-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140508043107/http://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1036436/000092962499001769/0000929624-99-001769.txt|dead-url=no}}</ref> Alcatel-Lucent（之前的Alcatel）于1999年底以15亿美金亿认股Genesys。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1999/09/29/business/company-news-alcatel-plans-to-buy-genesys-for-1.5-billion.html|title=Alcatel plans to buy Genesys for $1.5 Billion|publisher=''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]''|date=1999-09-29|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2015-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150527105620/http://www.nytimes.com/1999/09/29/business/company-news-alcatel-plans-to-buy-genesys-for-1.5-billion.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

之后，Genesys 于2001年收购了IBM CallPath的资产，计算机电话整合系统 (CTI)。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gartner.com/doc/330178/genesys-acquisition-ibms-callpath-allow |title=Genesys' Acquisition of IBM's CallPath Will Allow Both to Focus |date=2001-05-16 |accessdate=2014-06-30 |archive-date=2014-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141231160642/https://www.gartner.com/doc/330178/genesys-acquisition-ibms-callpath-allow |dead-url=no }}</ref> 而后于2002年，借着收购总部位于加州坎贝尔的Telera，该公司增加了其语音门户和交互式语音应答（IVR）系统。<ref>{{cite news|title=Genesys delivers self-service voice app Alcatel subsidiary joins call center rivals in adding VoiceXML support|author=Ann Bednarz|date=2002-08-05|publisher=Network World}}</ref> 并在2006年收购了GMK和VoiceGenie，Genesys进一步扩大其语音门户和交互式语音应答（IVR）系统。<ref>{{cite news|title=Alcatel's Genesys to Acquire VoiceGenie|date=2006-04-15|publisher=Telecom Tactics Insider}}</ref>

2007年10月，Paul Segre 继任 Wes Hayden 成为Genesys的首席执行官（CEO）。他而后并担任该公司的首席营运官（COO）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.destinationcrm.com/Articles/CRM-News/CRM-Featured-News/Genesys-CEO-Leaves-for-Nuance-Post-42882.aspx|title=Genesys CEO Leaves for Nuance Post|author=Leonard Klie|publisher=Destination CRM|date=3 October 2007-10-03|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2015-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120220206/http://www.destinationcrm.com/Articles/CRM-News/CRM-Featured-News/Genesys-CEO-Leaves-for-Nuance-Post-42882.aspx|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 两个月后，即 2007年12月，Genesys收购Informiam，一家以绩效管理软件来经营客户服务的软件开发公司。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.destinationcrm.com/Articles/CRM-News/Daily-News/Genesys-Acquires-Informiam-46930.aspx|title=Genesys Acquires Informiam|author=Phillip Britt|publisher=Destination CRM|date=2007-12-11|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2014-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141231134009/http://www.destinationcrm.com/Articles/CRM-News/Daily-News/Genesys-Acquires-Informiam-46930.aspx|dead-url=yes}}</ref> Genesys在2008年又收购了两家公司：Conseros和SDE软件开发工程公司。<ref name=telecomworldwire>{{cite news|title=Genesys acquires Conseros|date=2009-01-23|publisher=Telecomworldwire}}</ref><ref name=telecomworld>{{cite news|title=Genesys announces acquisition of SDE Software Development Engineering GmbH|date=2009-01-29|publisher=Telecomworldwire}}</ref> Conseros从事高容量工作项目管理软件开发;<ref name=telecomworldwire/> SDE专于创建主机管理软件。<ref name=telecomworld/>

2012年2月，Permira 基金以15亿美金从Alcatel-Lucent接盘，成为 Genesys的最大股东。<ref name=sfbizjournals2/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/bc0fd89e-fa49-11e0-b70d-00144feab49a.html#axzz30qzv0ELF|title=Alcatel-Lucent sells Genesys for $1.5bn|publisher=Financial Times|date=2011-10-19|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2013-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130925131451/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/bc0fd89e-fa49-11e0-b70d-00144feab49a.html#axzz30qzv0ELF|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2012年底，Genesys 收购LM Sistema, 一家开发IVR系统的巴西企业。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.destinationcrm.com/Articles/CRM-News/Daily-News/Genesys-Acquires-LM-Sistemas-a-Brazilian-Self-Service-Apps-and-Service-Provider-83565.aspx|title=Genesys Acquires LM Sistemas, a Brazilian Self-Service Apps and Service Provider|publisher=Destination CRM|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2014-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141231133729/http://www.destinationcrm.com/Articles/CRM-News/Daily-News/Genesys-Acquires-LM-Sistemas-a-Brazilian-Self-Service-Apps-and-Service-Provider-83565.aspx|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 

Genesys在2013年收购了五家公司。一月，收购Utopy，语音分析和企业人力资源优化提供商。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.destinationcrm.com/Articles/CRM-News/Daily-News/Genesys-Acquires-Utopy-87437.aspx|title=Genesys to buy Echopass in contact center deal|author=Cromwell Schubarth|publisher=''Silicon Valley Business Journal''|date=2013-10-08|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006114238/http://www.destinationcrm.com/Articles/CRM-News/Daily-News/Genesys-Acquires-Utopy-87437.aspx|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 一个月后，它再收购了Angel，提供IVR和呼叫中心软件云服务的供应商。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/ericsavitz/2013/02/26/microstrategy-to-sell-angel-com-unit-to-genesys-for-110m/ |title=MicroStrategy To Sell Angel.com Unit To Genesys For $110M |date=2013-02-26 |work=Forbes |first=Eric |last=Savitz |accessdate=2014-07-01 |archive-date=2019-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190424181422/https://www.forbes.com/sites/ericsavitz/2013/02/26/microstrategy-to-sell-angel-com-unit-to-genesys-for-110m/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2013年5月，公司又收购SoundBite Communications，该企业有1亿美元营收，负责提供云端收集和支付、移动营销和客户服务软件。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://online.wsj.com/article/BT-CO-20130520-711169.html |title=Genesys to Buy SoundBite for $100.4 Million |date=2013-05-20 |work=The Wall Street Journal |accessdate=2014-07-01 |archive-date=2013-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020072842/http://online.wsj.com/article/BT-CO-20130520-711169.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 另外，在当年10月，Genesys也收购了Echopass，云端的客户关系管理软件开发商。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/sanjose/news/2013/10/08/genesys-to-buy-echopass-in-contact.html|title=Genesys to buy Echopass in contact center deal|author=Cromwell Schubarth|publisher=''Silicon Valley Business Journal''|date=2013-10-08|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006111947/http://www.bizjournals.com/sanjose/news/2013/10/08/genesys-to-buy-echopass-in-contact.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 最后，12月，因公司进一步收购人力资源优化厂商Voran Technologia，Genesys的业务扩大到拉丁美洲。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://finance.yahoo.com/news/genesys-acquires-voran-technologia-deliver-170000754.html |title=Genesys Acquires Voran Technologia to Deliver Comprehensive Customer Experience Offering in Brazilian Market |date=2013-12-02 |accessdate=2014-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006115039/http://finance.yahoo.com/news/genesys-acquires-voran-technologia-deliver-170000754.html |archivedate=2014-10-06 }}</ref>

在2014年1月，Genesys收购了Ventriloquist Voice Solutions，提供云端多渠道客户沟通和互动软件的加拿大公司。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.speechtechmag.com/Articles/News/Speech-Technology-News-Features/Genesys-Further-Ventures-into-the-Cloud-with-Ventriloquist-Acquisition-94347.aspx|title=Genesys Further Ventures into the Cloud with Ventriloquist Acquisition|author=Leonard Klie|publisher=Speech Technology|date=2014-01-21|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2015-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150507130442/http://www.speechtechmag.com/Articles/News/Speech-Technology-News-Features/Genesys-Further-Ventures-into-the-Cloud-with-Ventriloquist-Acquisition-94347.aspx|dead-url=yes}}</ref> Ventriloquist早先曾是Genesys的合作伙伴。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://loyalty360.org/resources/article/genesys-adds-scale-with-acquisition-of-ventriloquist-voice-solutions|title=Genesys Adds Scale with Acquisition of Ventriloquist Voice Solutions|author=Jim Tierney|publisher=loyalty360|date=2014-01-22|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2015-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150316105020/http://loyalty360.org/resources/article/genesys-adds-scale-with-acquisition-of-ventriloquist-voice-solutions|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 同月底，公司也收购了Solariat，经营社交客户服务与分析平台的公司。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cloudcallcenterresource.com/topics/cloud-call-center/articles/368094-wheelings-dealings-genesys-expands-offerings-with-voice-solutions.htm|title=Wheelings and Dealings: Genesys Expands Offerings with Voice Solutions Acquisition|author=Rory J. Thompson|publisher=Cloud Call Center|date=2014-01-27|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812190445/http://www.cloudcallcenterresource.com/topics/cloud-call-center/articles/368094-wheelings-dealings-genesys-expands-offerings-with-voice-solutions.htm|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

在2014年5月，Genesys收购OVM Solutions，自动化讯息通讯公司。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.speechtechmag.com/Articles/News/Speech-Technology-Digest/Genesys-Acquires-OVM-Solutions-96797.aspx|title=Genesys Acquires OVM Solutions|publisher=Speech Technology Magazine|date=2014-05-05|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2015-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150507203553/http://www.speechtechmag.com/Articles/News/Speech-Technology-Digest/Genesys-Acquires-OVM-Solutions-96797.aspx|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在2014年9月，Genesys收购了Canaplus Consulting,语音集成公司，提升了其在东南亚地区的服务质量。

